parts.text: Create content for a slide about our excellent on-the-job training.

Headline: Hands-On Learning: Our Path to Expertise

Body: Our comprehensive on-the-job training program empowers employees with practical skills and real-world experience. This immersive approach ensures rapid development and fosters a culture of continuous learning and growth.

An illustration in a flat, geometric, corporate Memphis diagrammatic style. No text in the image. The scene depicts a vibrant on-the-job training environment within a stadium. A stylized figure wearing overalls and a baseball cap is actively learning, holding a large wrench, with a toolbox nearby. The background features elements of a stadium: bright, geometric stadium lights, a lush green field with subtle yardage indicators, and playful, scattered popcorn kernels. Surrounding the figure are abstract, floating sports elements like a soccer ball, a baseball glove, and a football. The overall color palette is dominated by corporate purple (#BF40BF), bright green (#DAF7A6), and warm sunset colors (oranges, yellows, pinks), creating a clever and charming atmosphere of learning and expertise.
